Project Workflows

Interactive Animated AI Companions for Children

1. Child Interaction Workflow (Main Loop)

Goal: Fun, natural conversation with animated reactions

Flow:

Child opens the app

Selects an animated character (Crow / Turtle / Cow)

Character greets the child with animation + voice

Character asks a question / tells a joke

Child responds (voice or buttons)

System:

Converts voice ‚Üí text

Detects emotion & intent

AI generates a safe, funny response

Reaction engine:

Chooses facial expression

Plays animation

Character replies with voice + expression

Loop continues until session ends

2. Voice Interaction Workflow

Goal: Smooth voice-based conversation

Flow:

Child presses ‚ÄúSpeak‚Äù or auto-listen starts

Microphone captures voice

Speech-to-Text processes input

Noise & safety filters applied

Text sent to AI engine

AI response returned

Text-to-Speech generates character voice

Audio synced with facial animation

Response played to child

3. Emotion & Reaction Workflow

Goal: Make characters feel alive

Flow:

Child response received

Emotion analyzer checks:

Tone

Speed

Keywords

Emotion classified (happy / confused / excited)

Reaction mapping engine selects:

Facial expression

Body animation

Voice tone

Animation & voice triggered together

Follow-up dialog selected

4. Safety & Moderation Workflow

Goal: 100% child-safe experience

Flow:

Child input received

Content filter scans input

If safe:

Continue to AI processing

If unsafe or unclear:

Block content

Trigger safe fallback response

Log incident (anonymous)

Notify parent dashboard (if required)

5. Learning Activity Workflow

Goal: Fun + hidden education

Flow:

Character introduces a mini activity

Child answers

System evaluates correctness

Character reacts:

Correct ‚Üí celebration animation üéâ

Wrong ‚Üí encouraging funny response

Hint or retry offered

Reward issued (sticker / sound)

Progress stored

6. Reward & Progress Workflow

Goal: Motivation and retention

Flow:

Interaction completes

Engagement score calculated

Reward unlocked

Visual celebration animation

Reward stored in profile

New content unlocked (optional)

7. Parent Control Workflow

Goal: Trust and transparency

Flow:

Parent logs in

Views child dashboard

Sees:

Usage time

Activities completed

Sets:

Time limits

Allowed characters

Changes saved

Rules enforced in real time

8. Admin Content Management Workflow

Goal: Easy updates without redeploy

Flow:

Admin logs in

Manages characters

Uploads:

Dialog templates

Animations

Voice styles

Sets age rules & difficulty

Publishes content

Content goes live instantly

9. Error & Fallback Workflow

Goal: Never break the child experience

Flow:

System error detected (AI / voice / network)

Fallback response triggered:

‚ÄúOops! My beak got tired üòÑ‚Äù

Character plays funny idle animation

Retry or switch to button mode

Error logged silently

10. Session Start & End Workflow
Session Start

App launched

Parental rules loaded

Character selected

Welcome animation played

Session End

Time limit reached or exit

Character says goodbye

Progress saved

Parent notified (optional)
